ence to the real name of the villain in \"Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles\" Shredder."],"history":"","mainAttribute":"Universal","baseStats":{"damage":"7 11","armor":0.0,"mana":"75","attackSpeed":"(1.7s BAT)","health":"120","movementSpeed":285},"talents":{"hero_talents":[{"talent_lvl":"25","talent_right":"Second Chakram","talent_left":"+1125 Timber Chain Range"},{"talent_lvl":"20","talent_right":"+20% Magic Resistance","talent_left":"+4% Chakram Slow"},{"talent_lvl":"15","talent_right":"+2.5% Whirling Death Stat Loss","talent_left":"+6 Reactive Armor Stacks and Duration"},{"talent_lvl":"10","talent_right":"+200 Health","talent_left":"+1.5 Mana Regen"}]}}